{"tid":1333504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"過左咁耐，究竟堅持「撤回」仲有咩意義？","createTime":"2019-07-19T17:18:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T18:08:02.000Z","uid":122234,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c82bf117807fb676823218571541dcf74d8513c4","tid":1333504,"uid":122234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:18:26.000Z","msg":"大家身邊既藍絲、父母永遠離唔開以下幾個論點：<br />\n<br />\n你又唔係罪犯，送中關你鬼事咩？<br />\n你係棋黎咋，你只不過比驚比送中既政客煽動咋！<br />\n政府都話左唔推啦，跟本就係一班暴民發洩。<br />\n<br />\n「徹回」係69、612既時候，的確係整場運動既核心，為左「徹回」兩個字，我地犧牲左幾多心血、甚至義士。<br />\n<br />\n但係隨着我地既革命，五大訴求出現左，我地運動既核心，再唔係「逃犯條例」本身，而係一系列我地要求政府回應既事。「送中」已經由主線，變左做一條支線。我地既目標唔再只係林鄭、李家超，而係延伸到警隊同一班必須要負責既狗官。<br />\n<br />\n其實我地堅持左1個半月，大家心入面都明白政府重推條例可能性好低，因為咁，「逃犯條例」本身漸漸係運動入面既重要性越黎越低。咁點解我地仲雖要執着於「徹回」？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因為我地爭取緊既意義，已經係送中條例本身之上</span></span><br />\n<br />\n逃犯條例一直係一個象徵，象徵住中共對我地既壓迫。無錯，送中好似同我地大眾無直接關係，我地確實唔大機會會被送中。我地之所以要革命，唔只係因為我地驚通過條例會威脅到自己人身安全，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而係要同中共政權講，我地絕對唔會屈服係你既壓迫下</span>。如果我地今次唔係反送中挺身而出，中共只會越黎越囂張，唔放我地在眼內。我地既焦點，一直係政權本身！<br />\n<br />\n之所以堅持「徹回」，<span style=\"color: red;\">係因為我地要政府屈服於香港市民！</span>我地唔要一個仍然比中共操控既政府，而係要一個完全由香港人聲音管治既政府。一日林鄭唔講徹回，一日政府都係比中共操控緊，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地都絕對唔會收手！</span><br />\n<br />\n我地721出黎，唔係純粹為「徹回」，而係背後象徵住我地對民主同獨立政府既要求，呢種情操都係點解我地經常同法國大革命。我地每一個人都係用緊我地既身軀，用抗爭寫下香港既歷史，係世界上能夠抵抗獨裁政權既事跡。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家諗通我地爭取緊既唔只係「徹回」既條例本身，而係佢象徵緊既自由同民主，我地聽日既抗爭將會更加有意義更加有目標。係嗌緊「徹回逃反條例」、「林鄭落台」既時候，我希望大家諗下諗我地心入面最底層爭取緊既係咩。"},{"pid":"320ab87fe42fbf0a91395569e3474bc45838fd2c","tid":1333504,"uid":92230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:19:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\n「緊急號召」臨時立法會計劃書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1333063\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1333063</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【臨時議會】非法呀！出解放軍呀！冇人理你呀！未係時機呀！等外國支持呀！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332681\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1332681</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n成立臨時議會嘅時機，唔係等出嚟，係人民自己一手一腳造出嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1333314\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1333314</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［721］認受性低都一定要宣布成立臨時立法會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1330843\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1330843</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n7月21日   時代革命 成立臨時政府<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1331101\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1331101</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n重奪會將揭抗爭新一章，立刻準備manifesto!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1271540\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1271540</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[必須廣傳] 7.21 三點開記招！7.21 三點開記招！7.21 三點開記招！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329992\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329992</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[學術派] 組成國民議會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1289796\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1289796</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n發夢寫咗一部香港憲法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327495\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n開始集體草擬一份屬於香港嘅民主憲法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1324231\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1324231</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>成立議會<br />\n已經係好多人嘅心聲<br />\n<br />\n721 新香港</strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"50e6fd808a3b2c44b23032728ea141e3b24f1f2d","tid":1333504,"uid":44870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:19:51.000Z","msg":"撤回意義大於一切, 所以不撤不散"},{"pid":"e98063469ec47f866120b608317fa2d1fadaa656","tid":1333504,"uid":491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:21:47.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"1ef3937207b8f17da575f695be793af1981bd64c","tid":1333504,"uid":122234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:21:52.000Z","msg":"聽日齊齊發個好夢"},{"pid":"070400e01233d081ec427d45f03b2f20b29d9a6c","tid":1333504,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:22:33.000Z","msg":"我要中共倒台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524b49ab7fbe6f28a9419c3a4a5b9a3b34c6a0bf","tid":1333504,"uid":122234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:24:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f7dd40a4cbfd399021a1074640b2632c481b5e6","tid":1333504,"uid":281388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:24:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你又唔係罪犯，送中關你鬼事咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n這是鐫刻在美國波士頓「猶太人屠殺紀念碑上」上的，德國新教牧師馬丁&middot;尼莫拉  Martin Niem&ouml;ller (1892-1984) 的懺悔詩。尼莫拉曾是納粹的受害者，他在晚年為自己當年的道德污點寫下懺悔詩。<br />\n<br />\n在德國，起初他們追殺共產主義者， <br />\n我沒有說話&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;因為我不是共產主義者； <br />\n接著他們追殺猶太人， <br />\n我沒有說話&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;因為我不是猶太人； <br />\n後來他們追殺工會成員， <br />\n我沒有說話&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;因為我不是工會成員； <br />\n此後他們追殺天主教徒， <br />\n我沒有說話&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;因為我是新教教徒； <br />\n最後他們奔向我來， <br />\n卻再也沒有人站出來為我說話。 <br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://m.xuite.net/blog/hslchurch/twblog/119379099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.xuite.net%2Fblog%2Fhslchurch%2Ftwblog%2F119379099&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83J9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=fa3eef34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.xuite.net/blog/hslchurch/twblog/119379099</a><br />\n<br />\n721 見"},{"pid":"5f08a3aaac7534f95a413010cd5c5fbb5a450f69","tid":1333504,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:25:05.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"31905b5725d9bea552bb0b6b22402650114e71ae","tid":1333504,"uid":122234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:27:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5070a681850fd64551f3f1ff7df8df45dfa6e6c","tid":1333504,"uid":122234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9815fba33c09f4b3bdf444a3732647e2ebfa9930","tid":1333504,"uid":36742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:33:40.000Z","msg":"依家反緊既係政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n721港島見。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 七大訴求 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」</code></pre>"},{"pid":"bc3dac7c851f34aa3fa9dcd73fccb566f8092f43","tid":1333504,"uid":122234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:35:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"667c49af4b17bbeeb8e5026a3097ca837be0a5a2","tid":1333504,"uid":122234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:39:15.000Z","msg":"我地要反抗政權"},{"pid":"93fabf2023223b0bf1fbfaaf008d4502b6877845","tid":1333504,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:40:36.000Z","msg":"係你先得閒應佢地<br />\n幫你推一下啦"},{"pid":"75cc2c0e3c216fbec512cb19ae7131a53ace5e06","tid":1333504,"uid":122234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:43:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2fdbc47e75c906ed5edc2227bbe0555819b8f143","tid":1333504,"uid":122234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:59:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3af45e5ce10d88d3ea2a8c0f4937b9cd33d03e28","tid":1333504,"uid":258377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:04:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721 見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我無嘢講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yh6HVQW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYh6HVQW.png&h=ecd1b383&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abdf81c050b486af9798cabc5d0f19dd700a7210","tid":1333504,"uid":122234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:08:02.000Z","msg":"推"}]}